Lingua/TR/Hyphenate version 0.01
================================

This module provides an implementation of a hyphenator
for Turkish. The algorithm is deterministic and can be
found at http://www.ripe.net/home/engin/heceler.html

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

